description: Introducing the first urban ice cream bus to hit the curbs of Houston and with its selection of handcrafted artisan ice cream (with vegan options available), handmade pops, ice cream sandwiches, floats, etc…everyone’s hearts have certainly been won. Locally sourced & 100% real ingredients are used to make each sweet offering at Chocolate Wasted. A few of the whimsically delicious flavors you’ll find include Fig Vanilla, Banana Pudding, Churro Donut, Lemon Pie, and many more. The ice pops are fabulously fruity and the floats are as delightfully fizzy & creamy as can be. With all this and more, give your guests at your next event a taste of these super delicious scoops by having Chocolate Wasted come out to you!
name: Chocolate Wasted
